languages.text: "Ты жив, сенешаль. Значит, дисциплина нашего отряда спасена. Единственная хорошая новость за последний час".

traits.locale_text: "Ты жив, сенешаль. Значит, дисциплина нашего отряда спасена. Единственная хорошая новость за последний час".

languages.text: "You are alive, Seneschal. I guess that means that the discipline in our squad is saved. That's the first good news we've had in the past hour."

languages.text: 「家令長、生きていたか。これで俺たちの部隊の規律は保たれるな。この一時間で初めての朗報だ」
languages.original_text: "You are alive, Seneschal. I guess that means that the discipline in our squad is saved. That's the first good news we've had in the past hour."

traits.locale_text: 「家令長、生きていたか。これで俺たちの部隊の規律は保たれるな。この一時間で初めての朗報だ」

languages.text: "Ihr lebt, Truchsess. Das bedeutet wohl, dass die Disziplin in unserem Trupp gerettet ist. Das ist die erste gute Nachricht in der letzten Stunde."
languages.original_text: "You are alive, Seneschal. I guess that means that the discipline in our squad is saved. That's the first good news we've had in the past hour."

traits.locale_text: "Ihr lebt, Truchsess. Das bedeutet wohl, dass die Disziplin in unserem Trupp gerettet ist. Das ist die erste gute Nachricht in der letzten Stunde."

languages.text: « Vous êtes vivant, sénéchal, ce qui veut dire que la discipline de notre escouade est sauve. Enfin une bonne nouvelle. »
languages.original_text: "You are alive, Seneschal. I guess that means that the discipline in our squad is saved. That's the first good news we've had in the past hour."

traits.locale_text: « Vous êtes vivant, sénéchal, ce qui veut dire que la discipline de notre escouade est sauve. Enfin une bonne nouvelle. »

languages.text: «Sigue vivo, senescal. Supongo que eso significa que la disciplina volverá a imperar en nuestra escuadra. Es la primera buena noticia que recibimos en una hora».

languages.text: “你还活着，总领，我猜这意味着小队的纪律有了保障。这么长时间过去了，这是我们得到的第一个好消息。”
languages.original_text: "You are alive, Seneschal. I guess that means that the discipline in our squad is saved. That's the first good news we've had in the past hour."

traits.locale_text: “你还活着，总领，我猜这意味着小队的纪律有了保障。这么长时间过去了，这是我们得到的第一个好消息。”

languages.text: "Hayatta olduğunu görmek güzel Seneşal. Demek ki mangamızda disiplin sürüyor. Bu, yakın zamanda aldığımız en iyi haber."
